<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="../style.css" />
  <title>Profile</title>
</head>

<body>
  <section class="main">
    <div class="bgbox">
      <div class="title"><strong>Welcome!</strong></div>

      <div class="subbox">
        <div class="subtext">
          <form action="/confirm" method="POST">
            It looks like it's your first time here :)<br><br>

            First, make sure the following information is correct:<br>
            Name: <strong>
              <%=locals.name%>
            </strong><br>
            Username: <strong>
              <%=locals.username%>
            </strong><br>
            <br>
            Next, please input your email: <br>
            <input type="email" name="email" id="email" maxlength="100" required></input>
            <br><br>
            Finally, please set a passphrase. Note that this passphrase will not be encrypted and will only be used to
            do
            things that are not so deep, such as if you ever want to delete your account. You will still log in through
            Ion OAuth. <br>
            <input type="text" name="pass" id="pass" maxlength="100" required></input>
            <br>
            <br>
            After all information is correct, click confirm to proceed.
            <br><br>
            <div class="cnt_buttons">
              <button class="button" type="submit">Confirm</button>
            </div>
          </form>



        </div>
      </div>

      <form class="submit" action="/grade/logout" method="POST">

      </form>
    </div>


  </section>

</body>

</html>
